SUMMARY:Speed Dating for Ppl Who Always Need a Trip Booked [28-35 yo] | Men
  & Women | Capitol Hill
LOCATION:Sugar Hill\, Seattle\, WA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\n​​🗣️🗣️ Calling you over if this e
 vent falls between trips on your calendar 🗣️🗣️\n\nIT'S SUMMER\, 
 aka time to get off the apps and into the city—join us for an evening of
  low-key speed dating! Bonus: your night out for the plot also supports Su
 gar Hill\, a local BIPOC-owned business at the same time. Win win.\n\n​
 ​❓Who is this event for? ❓\n\nAll of our events are made for BIPOC-i
 dentifying folks in the Greater Seattle area! This evening in particular i
 s for men and women (ages 28-35) that constantly need a trip booked to fee
 l ✨truly alive✨!\n\nCome compare destination and itinerary notes and m
 aybe find your future travel partner.\n\n❓ How does it work? ❓\n\nMix 
 Mix speed dating events run without an in-person host announcing table swi
 tches on a mic and definitely no nametags. Instead\, your evening is guide
 d virtually (via text!) and we set you up on meet-cute style dates (i.e.\,
  "Your next date is named Arnold\, look for a football-shaped head with a 
 tiny hat\, and a blue sweater over red flannel").\n\nAt the end of the eve
 nt\, you review all your dates and tell us who you felt a potential connec
 tion with. If they also pick you\, we give them your first name and phone 
 number and then y'all take it from there!\n\n​​​​🎟️ How much 
 does it cost to Mix Mix? 🎟️\n\nThis will run you an $20 ticket plus a
 t least one drink at the bar. We don't include drinks with our ticket pric
 e because A) We don't want to restrict your bevvy choices\, and B) $$$ acc
 essibility. Drinks range from $8 to $16\, so we're leaving how much your n
 ight costs up to you. Maybe you want one! Maybe you want three! ¯\\_(ツ)
 _/¯ Just keep your consumption respectful!\n\n​​🌙 The night in a n
 utshell 🌙\n\nYou arrive\, check in\, and buy a drink to support our gra
 cious hosts for the night.\n\nYou have several 10-min dates with brief bre
 aks in between\, and we supply starter questions/topics so your evening is
  filled with thoughtful conversation.\n\nAt the end of the event\, we send
  you a form to review your dates and tell us who you liked!\n\nWe send you
 r matches within 24 hours.\n\n​​What we expect from you:\n\nBe open to
  all kinds of connections—not everyone is the love of your life but ever
 yone IS worthy of a chat.\n\nYou buy a drink to support our gracious hosts
  for the evening\, and thereby support a local BIPOC-owned business.\n\n
 ​​What you can expect from us:\n\nPrivacy! Only your first name and ph
 one number are shared with matches. Consent is everything—we're not shar
 ing your info with anyone unless the vibes are mutual.\n\nA chill time and
  some suggested convo topics for each date.\n\n​​Fine print:\n\nCancel
 lation policy: In order to respect everyone's time\, money\, and experienc
 e\, there are no refunds and cancellations permitted. Additionally\, if yo
 u are more than 5 minutes late\, you will be counted as a no-show. All no-
 shows incur a $50 fee. See our full terms and conditions.\n\nSMS disclosur
 e: By registering for this event\, you agree to receive transactional text
  messages from Mix Mix about this event\, including registration confirmat
 ions\, event reminders\, check-in instructions\, and match notifications. 
 Message frequency: 8-12 messages per event. Message and data rates may app
 ly. Reply HELP for help or STOP to opt out.\n\n​Learn more about Mix Mix
 :\n\nMix Mix 101\n\nEvent day FAQ\n\nCalendar: Mix Mix Socials\n\nHosts: M
 ix Mix | Speed Dating in Seattle\n\nVenue: Sugar Hill\n\nEvent page: https
 ://luma.com/0k8ddz0l
URL:https://luma.com/0k8ddz0l
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
