  what they're actually building and shipping right now. The AiGovOps Found
 ation is hosting this practitioner-focused meetup where district CIOs\, co
 mpliance officers\, and anyone managing AI risk in learning environments c
 an hear directly from the people in the trenches on what's working and whe
 re education AI governance is heading next.\n\nEvent page: https://luma.co
 m/gejh0nrq
