SUMMARY:The Carry x Wavekelly: Walk\, Shop & Matcha
LOCATION:Wavekelly\, Bainbridge Island\, WA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nGet ready for round two.\n\nWe're back on Bainb
 ridge Island with our friends at Wavekelly—\n\n✨ 2.5 mile island walk 
 + strength circuit by local fitness trainer\n🛍️ Shop Wavekelly's late
 st summer styles \n​💪 Try on + purchase The Carry weighted vests (2 c
 olors—sizes 1\, 2\, 3)\n🍵 Matcha by Vale + good vibes\n🎁 Special o
 ffers & free gifts with purchase\n\nLast year 50+ of you showed up. How ma
 ny can we round up this year? Bring a friend. Bring your vest and try on o
 urs. Mingle with the founders\, the community\, and other women who like t
 o move in style.\n\n🗓 Saturday\, July 11th\n⏰ 10:30 AM (depart for wa
 lk at 11:00AM)\n📍 Wavekelly > island waterfront > park strength circuit
  > back to Wavekelly\n\nRSVP now—let's move!\n\n—\n\n🚢 Getting to B
 ainbridge\n\nIf you're coming from Seattle\, take the 9:35 AM Seattle ferr
 y.\nYou’ll land around 10:05 and be at the store by 10:15—perfect for 
 our 10:30 AM start. If the ferry runs late\, no stress—we’ll wait for 
 you. Island locals—see you right on time 😉.\n\n​🚶‍♀️ The R
 oute\n\nWe’ll be walking a beautiful 2.5-mile route curated by Megan of 
 Wavekelly. Route Link📍 Stroller-friendly? Absolutely. You’ll just vee
 r off slightly before we hit the Sakai Trail (at 305 & High School Rd) and
  rejoin us at the new Sakai Park Tennis Courts for a group photo!\n\n​
 💪 Post-Walk Burn\n\nAfter the walk\, stick around for a 20-minute guide
 d strength session in the park led by Kristin DaFoe from Lighthouse Fitnes
 s. Think of it as the cherry on top—just the right kind of burn to leave
  you feeling strong and energized.\n\n📸 Photo + Video\n\nWe’ll have a
  photographer capturing our strong\, stylish community. Snap your own too 
 and don’t forget to tag us: @thecarry.co & @shopwavekelly\n\n​🎽 Don
 ’t Have a Vest?\n\nNo worries! We’re bringing a handful of samples—f
 irst come\, first serve—pass them along to another vestie\, and just mov
 e with us.\n\nCalendar: Personal\n\nHosts: The Carry Team\, Cortney Bigelo
 w\, Esther Sedgwick\, Megan Sanchez\n\nVenue: Wavekelly\n\nEvent page: htt
 ps://luma.com/sb4qxelw
URL:https://luma.com/sb4qxelw
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
