SUMMARY:Sessions: Seattle
LOCATION:Patagonia\, Seattle\, Washington
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\n1% for the Planet Sessions are designed to ins
 pire environmental action and grow our global movement. We're showing up i
 n local communities to engage with our members\, give back to environment
 al partners\, and inspire local businesses to join this incredible network
 . And we're bringing the energy to Seattle during PNW Climate Week. Are yo
 u with us?\n\nJoin us at Patagonia Seattle where you’ll:\n\nBe inspired 
 by powerful local partnership and impact stories\n\nMeet and support loca
 l environmental partners (Adventure Travel Conservation Fund\, Na'ah Illah
 ee Fund\, and NW Avalanche Center)\n\nHear about 1% for the Planet's visi
 on for the future\n\nEngage with 1% for the Planet member brands\n\nThis i
 sn't your average networking event. It's a casual\, meaningful space to ga
 ther with folks doing good work. Come solo or with friends - this event is
  open to the community!\n\nBecause we know that when our network comes tog
 ether\, incredible things happen.\n\nWhat to Expect:\n\nA relaxed\, welco
 ming happy hour vibe\n\nInspiring conversations\n\nA drink or two on us 
 🍻\n\nTickets:\n$35 each. The cost of your ticket raises money for 1% fo
 r the Planet.\n\nMembers: Ticket purchase will automatically be added towa
 rd your 1% commitment.\n\nPresented by:\n1% for the Planet\n\nCalendar: 1%
  for the Planet Sessions 2026\n\nHosts: 1% for the Planet Events Team\, PN
 W Climate Week\n\nVenue: Patagonia\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/7b1hbi2
 h
