SUMMARY:Seattle AI Meetup - Post Alley
LOCATION:Seattle\, WA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nSeattle devs\, let’s get better together. \n\
 nThis used to be a meetup about building web and mobile apps with React. A
 nd then we noticed that every talk was about AI. \n\nAnd people started bu
 ilding games\, and tools\, and terminals\, and models...\n\nSo now it's an
  AI meetup. \n\nWhether you are deeply skill-pilled or just AI curious -th
 is is the meetup to learn about practical use cases\, fascinating experime
 nts\, and new tools you should try.  Most importantly it's where you'll me
 et the people working in and on AI every day. \n\nWho should attend?\nAnyo
 ne trying to build software. This includes hardcore devs and the new gener
 ation of builders. \n\nSchedule\n\n5:00 PM — Doors Open + meet & mingle\
 n\n6:00 PM — Demos Start\n\nAfter — Q&A + networking\n\n🚪 Doors ope
 n at 5:00 PM\n🎬 Demos start at 6:00 PM\n\nCalendar: 𝝠 Expo.dev\n\nHo
 sts: dan\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/29jqt1nv
