SUMMARY:Don't just dream it\, Build it.
LOCATION:10400 NE 4th St ste 3100\, Bellevue\, WA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nJoin Seattle's product\, design\, engineering\,
  and AI leaders for an evening of drinks\, conversation\, and custom Nike 
 By You sneakers.\n\nYour team has adopted AI somewhere in the stack - Curs
 or\, Claude Code\, Figma\, you name it. ICs are moving faster\, but delive
 ry timelines haven't kept up. The time is disappearing somewhere in the co
 ordination layer that none of those tools were built to fix.\n\nOn July 15
 th\, Builder.io is hosting a group of senior product\, design\, engineerin
 g\, and AI leaders in Bellevue for drinks\, appetizers\, and candid conver
 sation about what's working and where time is going.\n\nEach attendee will
  design their own pair of Nike sneakers\, to be shipped or hand-delivered 
 upon completion. A reminder that the best products\, and the best experie
 nces are never one-size-fits-all. They’re built with context\, craft\, a
 nd collaboration.\n\nSpace is limited. RSVP to reserve your spot.\n\nCalen
 dar: Builder Live Events\n\nHosts: Steve\n\nVenue: 10400 NE 4th St ste 310
