 movement\, discover wellness brands\, and be part of a community that fost
 ers joy\, personal growth\, and well-being.\n\nBODYROK Seattle (@bodyrokse
 attle) is a modern fitness brand known for its high-intensity\, low-impact
  workouts. Blending strength training\, cardio\, and core-focused movement
 s\, BODYROK classes are designed to sculpt\, lengthen\, and strengthen the
  body in just 40–50 minutes.\n\nAll tickets are final sale and non-refun
 dable.\n\nRelease Agreements\n\nPhoto/Video Release: By registering and/or
  Waitinglisting for this event\, you consent to having your photo or video
  taken\, shared on public social platforms\, and used for marketing purpos
 es. If you would prefer not to have your picture or video taken\, please l
 et the organizers know onsite.\n\nHold Harmless Agreement: You understand 
 and agree that you are attending the event and do not hold the organizers 
 or affiliates liable for any damages or injuries you may incur during it.\
