  off Seattle Tech Week 2026 with an evening of great conversations\, delic
 ious bites\, and pickleball at Picklewood in Sodo — Seattle's ultimate r
 ecreation destination to rally\, relax\, and refuel.\n\nYou don’t need t
 o be a pickleball pro to join us. Come to play\, learn\, or simply enjoy t
