SUMMARY:Huge Annual Summer BBQ | AI House
LOCATION:AI House\, Seattle\, WA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nOK folks\, our biggest event of the year. You k
 now it's always a good time!!!\n\nWe’re pulling together 700+ AI people 
 — founders\, engineers\, investors\, researchers\, all of it — in one 
 place for Seattle Tech Week.\n\nThere’s gonna be music\, drinks\, some b
 ites\, and just a lot of running into people you didn’t plan to meet but
  are very glad you did. We’ll also have a science fair-style setup in ou
 r new fancy ballroom with some of the coolest startups being built in Seat
 tle right now 👀\n\nIt’s a party\, but also kinda the whole point\, br
 inging people together so you can actually learn\, discover new things\, a
 nd get more involved in what’s being built here.\n\nCome hang!!!\n\nScie
 nce Fair Teams TBA\n\nThanks to our sponsors: Google and JP Morgan!\n\nAbo
 ut Google Cloud:\n\nGo from idea to impact faster with Google Cloud\, the 
 AI hyperscaler for the agentic era. We are in a category of one\, combinin
 g a complete\, first-party stack with an open ecosystem to build your comp
 etitive edge. Apply for up to $350k in Google Cloud (and Gemini) credits.\
 n\nAbout JP Morgan:\n\nJ.P. Morgan serves startups and venture-backed high
 -growth companies\, founders and venture capital firms across the globe in
  industries like technology\, fintech\, disruptive commerce and internet\
 , life sciences\, climate tech and healthtech. The firm provides deep indu
 stry expertise\, local support\, comprehensive solutions and services and 
 a robust network of investors and partners to meet clients’ commercial\,
  investment and private banking needs. Learn more at jpmorgan.com/innovati
 oneconomy.\n\nCalendar: AI House Community Events\n\nHosts: AI House\, JP 
 Morgan\n\nVenue: AI House\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/92pyibuc
