SUMMARY:Seattle Tech Week: Casino Night for Founders\, Builders\, and Funde
 rs | MongoDB
LOCATION:The Ruins\, Seattle\, WA
DESCRIPTION:Source: Luma\n\nSeattle Tech Week\, MongoDB\, Madrona\, NVIDIA\
 , and Temporal are bringing together Seattle's top AI-native founders\, bu
 ilders\, and funders for a night to test your luck!\n\nJoin us at The Ruin
 s to close out Seattle Tech Week in style. ➡️\n\nWhat's on the table:\
 n🎰 ♠️♥️ Texas Hold'em Poker\, Roulette\, Blackjack & more!\n
 🍸 Food and drinks\n✨ A curated room of AI founders\, builders\, and s
 tartup funders\n🤝 Meaningful networking across Seattle's startup and ve
 nture ecosystem\n🏆 Exclusive prizes for the night's top chip earners!\n
 \nHow it works:\nEvery guest starts with an equal chip stack upon entering
  and can move freely between tables throughout the night. Play your hand a
 t poker\, blackjack\, roulette\, craps\, and more as you build your stack 
 and compete for top prizes awarded to the night's biggest chip earners.\n\
 nNeed more chips to stay in the action? You can reload by visiting one of 
 the partner tables in the networking lounge/bar\, then head back to the ga
 mes and keep playing.\n\nTournament Prize Structure:\n🥇 1st Place — N
 VIDIA RTX 4060\n🥈 2nd Place — Apple AirPods Max\n🥉 3rd Place — M
 eta Smart Glasses\n\nLearn more about your event hosts:\n\nMongoDB is a d
 ocument database with the scalability and flexibility that you want with t
 he querying and indexing that you need. Build\, scale\, and succeed with M
 ongoDB for Startups.\n\nMadrona is a venture capital firm that specializes
  in early-stage technology companies across the Pacific Northwest\, Bay Ar
 ea and beyond\n\nNVIDIA is tackling challenges no one else can solve. NVID
 IA's work ignited the era of modern AI and is fueling industrial digitaliz
 ation across markets\n\nTemporal is an open source platform that helps de
 velopers build\, orchestrate\, and scale resilient Enterprise and AI appli
 cations.\n\nDISCLAIMER:\n\nThis is a casino-style entertainment event for 
 networking purposes only. All chips are provided free of charge\, have no 
 cash value\, and cannot be bought\, sold\, or redeemed for money. In accor
 dance with Washington State law\, no rake will be taken\, no entry fees wi
 ll be collected\, and no cash prizes will be awarded.\n\nCalendar: MongoDB
 \n\nHosts: MongoDB\n\nVenue: The Ruins\n\nEvent page: https://luma.com/kz2
 lcdiy
